<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3336708>
    dc:description "FIGURE 22. Conganteon kolyadai Olmi, ♂ from South Africa, 29°39.23’S 30°27.41’E, in lateral view (A). Conganteon lymanorum Olmi, Copeland & Guglielmino, ♀ holotype in dorsal (B) and lateral (C) view. Conganteon vannoorti Olmi, ♂ holotype: dorsal view (D), lateral view (E); head and mesosoma in dorsal view (F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3336708/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3336706>
    dc:description "FIGURE 21. Conganteon vulcanicum Benoit, ♀ holotype in dorsal (A) and lateral view (B). Conganteon sp. ♂ in dorsal view (C). Conganteon kolyadai Olmi, ♂ from South Africa, 29°39.23’S 30°27.41’E, in dorsal view (D). Scale bar: A: 2.34 mm; B: 1.47 mm; C: 2.55 mm; D: 4.18 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3336706/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3336716>
    dc:description "FIGURE 26. Chelae of Conganteon species holotype. A: C. fisheri Olmi; B: C. kolyadai Olmi; C: C. lymanorum Olmi, Copeland & Guglielmino; D: C. townesi Olmi; E: C. transvaalense Olmi; F: C. vulcanicum Benoit. Scale bar: A: 1.08 mm; B: 1.10 mm; C: 0.88 mm; D: 0.89 mm; E: 1.25 mm; F: 0.78 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3336716/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3336718>
    dc:description "FIGURE 27. ♂ genitalia (A–E) and chela (F) of Conganteon species. A: C. hawleyi Olmi, Copeland & van Noort sp. nov, holotype; B: C. kolyadai Olmi, paratype from South Africa, East London; C: C. fisheri Olmi, paratype; D: C. sensitivum Olmi, Copeland & van Noort sp. nov., holotype; E: C. townesi Olmi, ♂ from Madagascar, 23°10.78’S 43°37.01’E; F: C. walkerense Olmi, holotype. Scale bar: A: 0.11 mm; B, D: 0.14 mm; C: 0.16 mm; E: 0.13 mm; F: 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3336718/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3336714>
    dc:description "FIGURE 25. Conganteon hawleyi Olmi, Copeland & van Noort sp. nov., ♂ holotype: habitus in dorsal (A) and lateral (B) view; head in frontal view (C); forewing (D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3336714/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3336840>
    dc:description "FIGURE 85. Habitus of Conganteon and Deinodryinus species. A: Conganteon sensitivum Olmi, Copeland & van Noort sp. nov., ♂ holotype in dorsal view. B: D. harinhalai Olmi, ♂ holotype in dorsal view. C, D: D. musingilai Olmi, Copeland & Guglielmino, ♂ holotype in lateral (C) and dorsal (D) view. E: D. namorokensis Olmi, ♂ holotype in dorsal view. F: D. nigropictus Olmi, Copeland & van Noort sp. nov., ♀ paratype in dorsal view. Scale bar: A: 2.35 mm; E: 2.77 mm; F: 3.8 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3336840/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

